|---|---|
| P0 | Add authN/authZ to `/users`; strip emails from default response |
| P0 | Add `helmet`, disable `x-powered-by`, add rate limiting |
| P1 | Add central error handler + request logging (`morgan`) |
| P1 | Set `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` before accepting bodies |
| P2 | Add graceful shutdown and bind to localhost behind a TLS proxy |
| P2 | Introduce `zod`/`joi` validation pattern before adding new routes |

